cs.IT, cs.MM, cs.NI, cs.SI, cs.CL 

This paper is primarily focused on the design of hybrid precoding algorithms for millimeter wave MIMO systems, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and multimedia (cs.MM). It also involves network infrastructure (cs.NI) and signal processing (cs.SI) aspects. Additionally, the paper proposes algorithms for matrix factorization, which is a common technique in natural language processing (cs.CL).
